<title>
Brake Fluid Replacement
</title>
<ptxt>
Change brake fluid as follows.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Drain existing fluid from brake system completely, fill system with specified fluid and carry out air purge operation.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
For air purging procedure, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B4106004">Air Bleeding of Brake System</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</servinfo>
